description:
Service Usage

The service is used to lodge citizenship applications into the citizenship processing system which have been captured through online channels.
readme:
Service Usage

The service is used to lodge citizenship applications into the citizenship processing system which have been captured through online channels.

Service Behaviour

The service follows the standard lodgement pattern which includes creating the application, matching or creating the client, registering identity documents and performing risk checks.

Transformation

Transformation exists on the ESB between enterprise and ICSE provider messages.
